import { parseReport } from '@/lib/visuals/parser'
import { PERSONA_TEMPLATE_CONFIGS } from '@/lib/constants/report-templates'

// ─── Test Data ───

const DOCTOR_REPORT = `# Project Diagnostic Report

**Generated by Full Stack Human AI — The Doctor**

---

## Patient summary

The user described a SaaS product stuck in development for 6 months.

## Diagnosis

**The core problem is a lack of clear product scope.** The team is building features without validating demand.

## Symptoms vs. root cause

| What it looks like | What's actually happening |
| --- | --- |
| "We keep missing deadlines" | Scope creep from undefined product boundaries |
| "The team is demotivated" | No visible progress because success isn't defined |
| "Users aren't engaging" | Building for imagined users, not real ones |

## Risk level

High

If nothing changes in the next 60 days, the runway will shrink to a point where pivoting becomes impossible.

## Recommended actions

1. **Define the MVP scope** — Strip the product to the 3 features that solve the #1 user pain point.
2. **Talk to 10 users this week** — Not surveys. Actual conversations about their workflow.
3. **Kill the roadmap** — Replace it with a 2-week experiment cycle.

## What the AI can't see

- Team dynamics and interpersonal conflicts
- Financial runway details
- The real Francois would run a half-day scope workshop with the founding team

---

_Full Stack Human — The real Francois goes deeper. He'd run a focused scope workshop with your team to align on what actually ships. [Book a call →](https://calendly.com/fullstackhuman)_`

